Killing

As the Poisoner, your kills are delayed.
Kill everyone to win.

  • Poison Cooldown
    • Set how long a Poisoner has to wait to poison a player
  • Poison Kill Delay
    • Set how long it takes for the Poisoned target to die
  • Can Vent
    • : the Poisoner has the ability to Vent
    • : the Poisoner cannot vent
